<h3>POST /api/payments/charge</h3>
<div>
  Charge
</div>
<b>Resource URL </b>
<div>
http://localhost:3000/api/payments/charge
</div>
<b>Example request</b>
<div>
  curl -X POST -H 'Authorization: Bearer auth_token' -d "amount=1&project_id=1" "http://localhost:3000/api/payments/charge"
  <br/>
  auth_token: jwt token of current user
</div>
